525
00:39:39,610 --> 00:39:41,250
President Lin.

526
00:39:43,030 --> 00:39:45,690
I've been in Huikang for seven years, haven't I?

527
00:39:48,200 --> 00:39:51,540
It's true! Huikang is like my home.

528
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:53,470
In the office,

529
00:39:53,470 --> 00:39:57,260
