540
00:41:31,890 --> 00:41:34,410
A total joke.

541
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,860
What do you mean?

542
00:41:39,650 --> 00:41:41,650
Loyalty isn't important.

543
00:41:41,650 --> 00:41:43,510
I'm not important, either.

544
00:41:44,760 --> 00:41:48,190
Luo Jia, can't you be so emotional?

545
00:41:48,190 --> 00:41:51,060
Training soldiers for a thousand days to use them for one moment.

546
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:53,360
You should know this saying, shouldn't you?

547
00:41:53,360 --> 00:41:57,030
